<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>Save Endangered Wildlife</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Save Endangered Wildlife</h1>
        <p>Your contribution can make a difference!</p>
    </header>

    <section id="content">
        <p>Welcome to our campaign to save endangered wildlife. Together, we can protect and preserve the beauty of our planet.</p>
        <p>Make a donation today to support our conservation efforts.</p>

        <div id="donation-form">
            <label for="amount">Donation Amount:</label>
            <input type="number" id="amount" placeholder="Enter amount" min="1" step="1" required>
            <button onclick="donate()">Donate Now</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Save Endangered Wildlife. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
